---
import Page from '../layouts/Page.astro';
import LeaderboardSection from '../components/LeaderboardSection.astro';
import PricingTable from '../components/PricingTable.astro';
---
<Page title="Padel Community India (PCI) — India's Structured Padel Subscription" description="Padel Community India (PCI) is India's first structured padel subscription network. Fixed courts, competitive players, no logistics. Just show up and play.">

<!-- HERO -->
<section class="hero" style="border-bottom: 1px solid var(--rule); padding-top: 3vh;">
  <div class="hero-bg-word">PADEL</div>
  <div style="position:relative;z-index:2;">
    <div class="hero-eyebrow">Padel Community India (PCI) · Est. 2026</div>
    <h1 class="hero-title">
      Play <span id="hero-shuffle" class="hero-shuffle">better.</span>
    </h1>
    <p class="hero-sub">
      India's first structured padel subscription.<br>
      Fixed courts. Competitive players. No logistics.<br>
      Show up and play. Morning or evening. Your city.
    </p>
    <div class="hero-actions">
      <a href="#locations" class="btn-primary">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="width:14px;height:14px;">
          <path d="M20 10c0 6-8 12-8 12S4 16 4 10a8 8 0 0 1 16 0z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/>
        </svg>
        Find your city
      </a>
      <a href="#how-it-works" class="btn-secondary">How it works</a>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- WHAT IS PCI -->
<section>
  <div class="section-label">What is PCI</div>
  <h2 class="what-headline">
    A subscription.<br>
    Not a booking.<br>
    <span>A commitment.</span>
  </h2>
  <div class="what-cols">
    <div class="what-col">
      <div class="what-col-rule"></div>
      <p>Finding good padel in India means paying walk-in rates every time.<br>
      Chasing four people to confirm.<br>
      Showing up to play with strangers at random skill levels.<br>
      PCI fixes all three.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="what-col">
      <div class="what-col-rule"></div>
      <p>We lock in courts at the best venues in each city.<br>
      Form <strong>groups of 24 intermediate and above players.</strong><br>
      You pay once, you show up, you play.<br>
      Same competitive people. No hassle.</p>
    </div>
    <div class="what-col">
      <div class="what-col-rule"></div>
      <p>Each group is <strong>venue-specific and timeslot-specific.</strong><br>
      Morning or late evening. Your city. Your venue.<br>
      When we fill a group, we open another.<br>
      City by city.</p>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- HOW IT WORKS -->
<section id="how-it-works">
  <div class="section-label">How it works</div>
  <div class="steps">
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">01</div>
      <div class="step-title">Choose your group</div>
      <div class="step-body">Find your city, your venue, and your timeslot.<br>Morning or late evening.<br>Each group has 24 spots.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">02</div>
      <div class="step-title">Subscribe</div>
      <div class="step-body">Pick a 1, 3, 6 or 12-month plan.<br>Pay upfront. Your spot is locked for the duration.<br>Longer plans get better rates.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">03</div>
      <div class="step-title">Register on Reclub</div>
      <div class="step-body">Join your private group on Reclub.<br>Register for each session. Vote on formats.<br>See who's playing. Track your stats.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="step">
      <div class="step-num">04</div>
      <div class="step-title">Show up and play</div>
      <div class="step-body">Courts ready. Balls fresh. Mineral water waiting.<br>Two 90-minute sessions per day.<br>Structured, competitive padel with people who take the game seriously.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- WHAT'S INCLUDED -->
<section>
  <div class="section-label">Every subscription includes</div>
  <div class="included-grid">
    <div class="included-item">
      <div class="inc-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#C8F54A" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><line x1="3" y1="12" x2="21" y2="12"/><line x1="12" y1="3" x2="12" y2="21"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="inc-title">Dedicated Courts</div>
        <div class="inc-desc">Fixed courts at your venue, locked for your group every session.<br>No booking. No hassle.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="included-item">
      <div class="inc-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#C8F54A" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><path d="M2.8 9a10 10 0 0 1 18.4 0"/><path d="M2.8 15a10 10 0 0 0 18.4 0"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="inc-title">Tournament-Grade Balls</div>
        <div class="inc-desc">Never more than 3 to 4 hours on the same balls.<br>You always play with balls that have bounce and feel.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="included-item">
      <div class="inc-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#C8F54A" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M8 2h8"/><path d="M9 2v2.789a4 4 0 0 1-.672 2.219l-.656.984A4 4 0 0 0 7 10.212V20a2 2 0 0 0 2 2h6a2 2 0 0 0 2-2v-9.788a4 4 0 0 0-.672-2.219l-.656-.984A4 4 0 0 1 15 4.789V2"/><line x1="7" y1="15" x2="17" y2="15"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="inc-title">Bottled Mineral Water</div>
        <div class="inc-desc">Waiting at the court every session.<br>Nothing to sort. Nothing to pay for.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="included-item">
      <div class="inc-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#C8F54A" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M17 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-4-4H5a4 4 0 0 0-4 4v2"/><circle cx="9" cy="7" r="4"/><path d="M23 21v-2a4 4 0 0 0-3-3.87"/><path d="M16 3.13a4 4 0 0 1 0 7.75"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="inc-title">Competitive Peers</div>
        <div class="inc-desc">Intermediate and above only.<br>Same faces every session.<br>Real partnerships. Real improvement.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="included-item">
      <div class="inc-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#C8F54A" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="inc-title">Reclub App Access</div>
        <div class="inc-desc">Register for sessions. Vote on formats.<br>Track stats. Chat with your group.<br>All in one place.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="included-item">
      <div class="inc-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#C8F54A" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="8" r="6"/><path d="M15.477 12.89L17 22l-5-3-5 3 1.523-9.11"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="inc-title">Tournaments &amp; Social Events</div>
        <div class="inc-desc">Internal tournaments seeded by your leaderboard ranking.<br>Once a month, the group gets together off the court.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="included-item">
      <div class="inc-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#C8F54A" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M15 10l4.553-2.069A1 1 0 0 1 21 8.82v6.36a1 1 0 0 1-1.447.889L15 14"/><rect x="1" y="6" width="15" height="12" rx="2"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="inc-title">Game Footage</div>
        <div class="inc-desc">Professional cameras on every court.<br>Watch sessions back. Track improvement.<br>Share highlights straight to social media.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
    <div class="included-item">
      <div class="inc-icon">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#C8F54A" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M22 11.08V12a10 10 0 1 1-5.93-9.14"/><polyline points="22 4 12 14.01 9 11.01"/></svg>
      </div>
      <div>
        <div class="inc-title">Welcome Kit</div>
        <div class="inc-desc">A curated set of personalised PCI goodies, sent to every new member when they join.</div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- FORMATS -->
<section id="formats">
  <div class="section-label">What we play</div>
  <div class="formats-grid">
    <div class="format-card">
      <div class="format-tag">Format</div>
      <div class="format-title">Americano</div>
      <div class="format-body">Rotating partners. Everyone plays with everyone.<br>Points-based. Competitive. Social.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="format-card">
      <div class="format-tag">Format</div>
      <div class="format-title">Mexicano</div>
      <div class="format-body">Paired with and against players at your level.<br>Scores update in real time. Always competitive.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="format-card">
      <div class="format-tag">Format</div>
      <div class="format-title">Spontaneous Tournaments</div>
      <div class="format-body">Fixed teams. Bracket play. Bragging rights.<br>Called when numbers are right and the energy demands it.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="format-card">
      <div class="format-tag">Session</div>
      <div class="format-title">Drills &amp; Practice</div>
      <div class="format-body">Serve patterns. Wall play. Volleys. Lobs.<br>Structured improvement. Not just match play.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="format-card">
      <div class="format-tag">Format</div>
      <div class="format-title">Open Doubles</div>
      <div class="format-body">Pick your partner. Challenge any pair.<br>Classic padel. On your terms.</div>
    </div>
    <div class="format-card">
      <div class="format-tag">Wildcard</div>
      <div class="format-title">Whatever the Night Calls For</div>
      <div class="format-body">Sometimes the group decides.<br>Format flexes around who shows up.</div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<LeaderboardSection />

<PricingTable subheadline="One price across all cities and venues. The longer you commit, the better the monthly rate. Everything included. No extras, no surprises." />

<!-- RECLUB -->
<section>
  <div class="section-label">The app</div>
  <div class="reclub-wrap">
    <div>
      <div style="width:120px;height:40px;background:var(--card);border:1px solid var(--rule);display:flex;align-items:center;justify-content:center;margin-bottom:28px;">
        <span style="font-size:9px;letter-spacing:0.15em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--muted);opacity:0.5;">Reclub logo</span>
      </div>
      <h2 class="reclub-headline">Everything runs<br>through <span>Reclub.</span></h2>
      <p class="reclub-desc">
        No WhatsApp chaos. No manual sign-up sheets. The subscription runs on <strong>Reclub</strong>, a dedicated app built exactly for sports groups like this one. Every subscriber gets access from day one.
      </p>
      <a href="https://reclub.co" target="_blank" rel="noopener" class="reclub-badge">
        <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#C8F54A" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="width:14px;height:14px;display:inline-block;vertical-align:middle;margin-right:4px">
          <rect x="5" y="2" width="14" height="20" rx="2"/><line x1="12" y1="18" x2="12.01" y2="18"/>
        </svg>
        Private group · Subscribers only
      </a>
    </div>
    <div class="reclub-features">
      <div class="reclub-feature">
        <div class="reclub-feature-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#C8F54A" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><circle cx="12" cy="12" r="10"/><polyline points="9 12 11 14 15 10"/></svg></div>
        <div><div class="reclub-feature-title">Register for tonight in one tap</div><div class="reclub-feature-desc">See who's confirmed, who's on the waitlist. No chasing, no confirming over chat.</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="reclub-feature">
        <div class="reclub-feature-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#C8F54A" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M14 9V5a3 3 0 0 0-3-3l-4 9v11h11.28a2 2 0 0 0 2-1.7l1.38-9a2 2 0 0 0-2-2.3H14z"/><path d="M7 22H4a2 2 0 0 1-2-2v-7a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h3"/></svg></div>
        <div><div class="reclub-feature-title">Vote on the format</div><div class="reclub-feature-desc">Mexicano or round robin? The group votes, the Day Leader locks it in.</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="reclub-feature">
        <div class="reclub-feature-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#C8F54A" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><polyline points="16 3 21 3 21 8"/><line x1="4" y1="20" x2="21" y2="3"/><polyline points="21 16 21 21 16 21"/><line x1="15" y1="15" x2="21" y2="21"/><line x1="4" y1="4" x2="9" y2="9"/></svg></div>
        <div><div class="reclub-feature-title">Team draws &amp; pairings</div><div class="reclub-feature-desc">Fair, random team divisions. No awkward picking, no same pairs every night.</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="reclub-feature">
        <div class="reclub-feature-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#C8F54A" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><line x1="18" y1="20" x2="18" y2="10"/><line x1="12" y1="20" x2="12" y2="4"/><line x1="6" y1="20" x2="6" y2="14"/></svg></div>
        <div><div class="reclub-feature-title">Stats &amp; history</div><div class="reclub-feature-desc">Sessions played, wins, partners. Your padel record, in one place.</div></div>
      </div>
      <div class="reclub-feature">
        <div class="reclub-feature-icon"><svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="#C8F54A" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/></svg></div>
        <div><div class="reclub-feature-title">Group chat</div><div class="reclub-feature-desc">Talk game, share clips, plan sessions. Without the WhatsApp noise.</div></div>
      </div>
    </div>
  </div>
</section>

<!-- CITIES / LOCATIONS -->
<section id="locations">
  <div class="section-label">Locations</div>
  <div style="margin-bottom:32px;">
    <h2 style="font-family:'Bebas Neue',sans-serif;font-size:clamp(32px,4vw,52px);letter-spacing:0.04em;line-height:1;margin-bottom:10px;">Where we operate</h2>
    <p style="font-size:14px;color:var(--muted);font-weight:300;max-width:480px;line-height:1.7;">Starting in Pune. More cities coming. Each city has its own page with venue details and available groups.</p>
  </div>
  <div class="cities-grid">

    <!-- PUNE — LIVE, not hyperlinked -->
    <div class="city-card" style="cursor:default;">
      <div class="city-image">
        <div class="city-image-placeholder">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="8.5" r="1.5"/><polyline points="21 15 16 10 5 21"/></svg>
          <span>Pune city image</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="city-body">
        <div class="city-name">Pune</div>
        <div class="city-venues" style="font-size:13px;color:var(--muted);font-weight:300;margin-bottom:8px;">Kharadi</div>
        <div style="margin-top:8px;">
          <a href="/pune" style="font-size:11px;font-weight:600;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;color:var(--lime);text-decoration:none;border-bottom:1px solid rgba(200,245,74,0.3);">View Pune →</a>
        </div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- MUMBAI -->
    <div class="city-card" style="cursor:default;">
      <div class="city-image">
        <div class="city-image-placeholder">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="8.5" r="1.5"/><polyline points="21 15 16 10 5 21"/></svg>
          <span>Mumbai city image</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="city-body">
        <div class="city-name" style="color:var(--muted);">Mumbai</div>
        <div class="city-venues">Coming soon</div>
        <div class="city-groups"><span class="city-coming">Venues TBA</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>

    <!-- BANGALORE -->
    <div class="city-card" style="cursor:default;">
      <div class="city-image">
        <div class="city-image-placeholder">
          <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5"><rect x="3" y="3" width="18" height="18" rx="2"/><circle cx="8.5" cy="8.5" r="1.5"/><polyline points="21 15 16 10 5 21"/></svg>
          <span>Bangalore city image</span>
        </div>
      </div>
      <div class="city-body">
        <div class="city-name" style="color:var(--muted);">Bangalore</div>
        <div class="city-venues">Coming soon</div>
        <div class="city-groups"><span class="city-coming">Venues TBA</span></div>
      </div>
    </div>

  </div>
</section>

<!-- CTA -->
<section class="cta-section">
  <h2 class="cta-headline">Ready to stop<br><span>hunting for courts?</span></h2>
  <p class="cta-sub">Find your city, pick your venue and timeslot, and apply for a spot. 24 subscribers per group. Once full, it's a waitlist.</p>
  <div class="cta-actions">
    <a href="/pune" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:14px 28px;font-size:12px;font-weight:700;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;text-decoration:none;background:var(--lime);color:var(--black);transition:opacity 0.2s;">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="width:14px;height:14px;"><path d="M20 10c0 6-8 12-8 12S4 16 4 10a8 8 0 0 1 16 0z"/><circle cx="12" cy="10" r="3"/></svg>
      Start with Pune
    </a>
    <a href="https://wa.me/918007306165" target="_blank" rel="noopener" style="display:inline-flex;align-items:center;gap:8px;padding:14px 28px;font-size:12px;font-weight:500;letter-spacing:0.1em;text-transform:uppercase;text-decoration:none;border:1px solid var(--rule);color:var(--muted);transition:color 0.2s,border-color 0.2s;">
      <svg viewBox="0 0 24 24" fill="none" stroke="currentColor" stroke-width="1.5" stroke-linecap="round" stroke-linejoin="round" style="width:14px;height:14px;"><path d="M21 15a2 2 0 0 1-2 2H7l-4 4V5a2 2 0 0 1 2-2h14a2 2 0 0 1 2 2z"/></svg>
      WhatsApp us
    </a>
  </div>
</section>

<script>
  const words = ['better.', 'consistently.', 'with your people.'];
  let current = 0;
  const el = document.getElementById('hero-shuffle');

  function next() {
    current = (current + 1) % words.length;

    el.classList.add('shuffle-out');

    setTimeout(() => {
      el.textContent = words[current];
      el.classList.remove('shuffle-out');
      el.classList.add('shuffle-in');

      setTimeout(() => {
        el.classList.remove('shuffle-in');
      }, 350);
    }, 350);
  }

  setInterval(next, 2400);
</script>

</Page>
